    "name": "Locomoto",
    "steam_appid": 2328650,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《乐客萌途》（Locomoto）是一款轻松惬意的生活模拟冒险火车游戏，而你将担任火车长！你可以定制、管理和扩展你的火车，同时照顾你那些多姿多彩、毛茸茸的乘客们。登上你的火车，开启一段穿越美丽风景的旅程，在此过程中，你将伴随着丰富的原创配乐，沉浸在舒缓柔和的Lofi节拍中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328650/extras/398fba22c86c239d5e13ca2bac2adb91.avif?t=1759310052\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328650/extras_big/398fba22c86c239d5e13ca2bac2adb91.avif?t=1759310052 width=800 height=58 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328650/extras/a0e779fa64b32d95ba3663a2f3850279.poster.avif?t=1759310052\" width=720 height=255 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328650/extras/a0e779fa64b32d95ba3663a2f3850279.webm?t=1759310052\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为你的乘客提供最佳的旅行体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >邀请乘客登上你的火车，帮助他们顺利抵达各自的目的地！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >照顾好你的乘客，确保他们旅途舒适。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >细心照料你的火车，为下一段旅程做好准备。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328650/extras/76649375cfccd287799aec3c12370d17.avif?t=1759310052\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328650/extras_big/76649375cfccd287799aec3c12370d17.avif?t=1759310052 width=800 height=58 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328650/extras/a86d98e20f9001f8ea7acec50e7e7316.poster.avif?t=1759310052\" width=720 height=255 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328650/extras/a86d98e20f9001f8ea7acec50e7e7316.webm?t=1759310052\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >定制专属于你的火车，运用多样的家具装饰车厢，打造独特的风格！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >运用从世界各处搜集的资源制作需要的家具，使用不同的材料来为它们赋予缤纷色彩。添加更多车厢来扩展你的火车，让更多乘客一起享受旅程！定制属于自己的形象！在丰富的动物特征和色彩之间挑选，尽情尝试在整个旅程中收集到的各式服装，进一步展现你独特的个性！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328650/extras/2c900b8809962aaeb5ad4ac59f9c94c2.avif?t=1759310052\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328650/extras_big/2c900b8809962aaeb5ad4ac59f9c94c2.avif?t=1759310052 width=800 height=58 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328650/extras/7fcc637be3bb4bcf1143bbb44a6ff0e8.poster.avif?t=1759310052\" width=720 height=255 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328650/extras/7fcc637be3bb4bcf1143bbb44a6ff0e8.webm?t=1759310052\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在世界中自由探索与互动，尽情体验与多样且独特的角色相处的乐趣。帮助这些角色实现他们的愿望，就能获得服装、资源以及制作用的设计图等奖励。随着与这些角色建立更深的友谊，你将更深入了解他们的个性，以及在这个世界中他们面临的困难。</p>",
